burst and post-outburst photometry, we infer that the\noutburst ejecta are evolving into a dense, highly structured circumstellar\nenvironment from precursor outbursts within years of the December 2016 event.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Jun 2017 21:46:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 12 Oct 2017 17:49:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-06"}
