ctively. We employed such high-resolution\ntechniques to volcanic glasses in ash particles of the 2010 Eyjafjallaj\\\"okull\neruption. Our results are well consistent with the previously reported data\nobtained at lower spatial resolution, supporting the reliability of the method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Jun 2017 11:09:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-03"}
