r gas, contamination\nfrom kinetic SZ ($\\sim 10\\%$), and the absolute calibration of the tSZ map\n($7\\%$). Investigation using a larger sample of clusters would help minimise\nthese effects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Jun 2017 14:56:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Jul 2017 23:19:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-11"}
